  "formulaSource": "Tree removal base pricing from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 national average surveys. Trunk diameter and condition multipliers derived from International Society of Arboriculture (ISA) risk assessment and pricing guidelines. Proximity surcharges from HomeAdvisor hazardous-access cost data. Stump removal and cleanup pricing from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 add-on service surveys. Regional labor multipliers derived from BLS OES regional wage data for tree trimmers and pruners (SOC 37-3013).",
